159
00:11:31,114 --> 00:11:32,533
Apakah kalian akan makan bersama?

160
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:34,102
Anggur dan…

161
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:37,598
Namaku Keju. Aku teman Anggur.

162
